</m:msub>
</m:mrow>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msup>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-52">
We note here that angular speeds of all particles constituting the body are same. Hence, the constant "1/2" and "
<m:math>
<m:msup>
<m:mi> ω </m:mi>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msup>
</m:math>
