</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-54">
However, we know that :
</para>
<para id="element-55">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
<m:mi> I </m:mi>
<m:mo> = </m:mo> 
