<m:mi> m </m:mi>
<m:mi> i </m:mi>
</m:msub>
<m:msup>
<m:mrow>
<m:msub>
<m:mi> r </m:mi>
<m:mi> i </m:mi>
</m:msub>
</m:mrow>
<m:mn> 2 </m:mn>
</m:msup>
</m:mtd>
</m:mtr>
</m:mtable>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-56">
Combining two equations, we have :
</para>
<para id="element-57">
<equation id="eq-57">
<m:math display="block">
<m:mtable columnalign="left">
<m:mtr>
<m:mtd>
