</m:math>
.
</para>
<para id="element-78">
<term>5.</term> Objects in rotation have rotational kinetic energy of rotation due to rotational motion of individual particles, constituting the object. 
</para>
<para id="element-79">
<term>6.</term> Object in pure rotation has only rotational kinetic energy i.e. no translational kinetic energy is involved. 
</para>
